<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Test Website</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00c6ff, #0072ff);
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 100px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 40px;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 18px;
    }

    .box {
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
      padding: 20px;
      margin: auto;
      width: 300px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="box">
    <h1>🚀 Website Test OK</h1>
    <p>Kalau nampak ni, web kau dah jalan!</p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
